OL,3,CLidl employee unfairly dismissed for
OL,4,Cnot having a degree is awarded #50k
OL,6,FHe worked as a senior construction
OL,7,Fconsultant in Doncaster where he was
OL,8,Fresponsible for overseeing the
OL,9,Fbuilding and refurbishment of regional
OL,10,Fstores before being made redundant in
OL,11,FMarch 2023.
OL,13,FMr Norman was first told of proposed
OL,14,Fredundancies during a meeting on 30
OL,15,FJanuary 2023 after which he discovered
OL,16,Fhe was among three construction
OL,17,Fconsultants up for redundancy with
OL,18,Fonly one role available as part of the
OL,19,Frestructure.
