OL,3,CLidl employee unfairly dismissed for
OL,4,Cnot having a degree is awarded #50k
OL,6,FThe other two consultants were both in
OL,7,Ftheir 30s at the time. After learning
OL,8,Fone of them had been successful in
OL,9,Fsecuring the job, Mr Norman met with
OL,10,Fhis line manager Liam Schofield who
OL,11,Finformed him he had been "marked down
OL,12,Ffor not having 'relevant construction
OL,13,Fqualifications' in that you do not
OL,14,Fhave a construction degree", the
OL,15,Ftribunal heard.
