OL,3,CLidl employee unfairly dismissed for
OL,4,Cnot having a degree is awarded #50k
OL,6,FMr Norman's argument that those in
OL,7,Ftheir 60s were "less likely" to have a
OL,8,Fdegree than those in their 30s was
OL,9,Faccepted by the tribunal that ruled
OL,10,Fthe inclusion of having a degree or
OL,11,Fconstruction qualification as part of
OL,12,Fthe redundancy selection criteria
OL,13,Famounted to indirect age
OL,14,Fdiscrimination.
