OL,6,FOf the effects of the redundancy on Mr
OL,7,FNorman, Judge Maidment said he had
OL,8,Fsuffered some "clear psychological
OL,9,Fdamage", evidenced by medication taken
OL,10,Fby the claimant and counselling he had
OL,11,Freceived.
OL,13,F"The impact on his family life had
OL,14,Fbeen extreme and at one point he had
OL,15,Fhad suicidal ideations," the judge
OL,16,Fadded.
