OL,3,CLidl employee unfairly dismissed for
OL,4,Cnot having a degree is awarded #50k
OL,6,FIn a remedy judgment published on May
OL,7,F9, the tribunal ordered Lidl to pay Mr
OL,8,FNorman #46,280.63 in compensation for
OL,9,Funfair dismissal and a further
OL,10,F#4,646.15 for injury of feelings
OL,11,Fbecause of indirect age discrimination.
OL,13,FThe ruling noted that the amount
OL,14,Fawarded for unfair dismissal had been
OL,15,Freduced by 50% to reflect the chance
OL,16,Fthat the claimant would have been
OL,17,Ffairly dismissed in any event.
